


» To determine the steady point, do:

	SSDeterminer ssd = new SSDeterminer(measurements, normalizationWindowSize, smoothingWindowSize, outlierFactor, sdWindowSize, sdOutlierThreshold)
	
	ssd.add(data)

	ssd.smoothOutput()

	ssd.computeAllSD()

	sPoint = ssd.detectSteadyPoint()


» Typical values for configuration parameters:

	+ measurements: 		
	+ normalizationWindowSize:	
	+ smoothingWindowSize:		
	+ outlierFactor:		
	+ sdWindowSize:			
	+ sdOutlierThreshold:		
